        "content": "<p>myunbin opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12925\">PR #12925</a> from <code>myunbin:main</code> to <code>bytecodealliance:main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This PR adds several arithmetic simplification rules:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>((x + y) - (x + z)) --&gt; (y - z)</code></li>\n<li><code>((x - z) - (y - z)) --&gt; (x - y)</code></li>\n<li><code>((x - y) - (x - z)) --&gt; (z - y)</code></li>\n<li><code>min(x, y) + max(x, y) --&gt; x + y</code></li>\n<li><code>((x - y) + (y + z)) --&gt; (x + z)</code></li>\n<li><code>(x - (x + y)) --&gt; -y</code></li>\n<li><code>(x + (y + (z - x))) --&gt; (y + z)</code></li>\n<li><code>(x + y) == (y + x) --&gt; true</code></li>\n<li><code>(x - y) != x --&gt; y != 0</code></li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>",
